snippet.title: Insta360 firmware cracked. You won't believe what they're hiding. (FPV News with JB and ItsBlunty)
snippet.description:
Uncertain about what to buy? Check out THE ULTIMATE FPV SHOPPING LIST: https://www.fpvknowitall.com/ultimate-fpv-shopping-list

SUPPORT ME ON PATREON at: http://bit.ly/2Ep5Sia

THIS IS MY FULL TIME JOB. Here are other ways that you can support me: https://www.fpvknowitall.com/support-me/

ItsBlunty's channel is:
https://www.youtube.com/c/ItsBlunty/

--- TABLE OF CONTENTS ---

0:00 - Intro music

3:00 - Show begins.

* Evan Turner (HeadsUpFPV) wins DRL Championship

9:01 - Insta360 One R misleading resolution and bitrate specs? And GPL violations?
* Reddit thread - https://bit.ly/2YAwJAG

23:36 - Sub-250g 4" long range with 3S LiIo and 35 minute flight time
* Instagram post -  https://bit.ly/3oBwT5u

DaveC FPV making progress on his 1S long range project
* Instagram post - https://bit.ly/39HPOHr

Emax Nanohawk 1S long range project
* RCGroups thread - https://bit.ly/3pJuZ4a

Ummagawd Sub250 five inch freestyle frame
* Ummagawd Store - https://bit.ly/3oGD48j

32:32 - Vic Moss calls for awareness of dangerous Mississippi drone laws
* https://dspalliance.org/mississippi-we-need-to-talk-about-drones/

41:30 - DJI Goggles V2 update.

50:29 - Gemfan Moonlight LED Props V2
* https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JGyqhIenFZw

52:27 - FETTEC F7 adds 14v regulator for HV video transmitters
* Instagram photo of new FC - https://i.imgur.com/NuXQSPy.jpg

55:06 - Community Spotlight: 3D printed folding TPU holder for Crossfire receiver
* Thingiverse - https://www.thingiverse.com/thing:4731250
* Thingiverse - https://www.thingiverse.com/thing:4662724

57:46 - Drone hits Chilean Navy helicopter with injury to pilot.
* https://mentourpilot.com/incident-drone-helicopter-collision-occupant-injury/

1:02:54 - PBS Terra episode on drone racing with Jordan Temkin (JetFPV)
* https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Pgj95EntvW0
